file.name: pets-custom-content-type.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: Swagger Petstore
  license:
    name: MIT
paths:
  /haljson:
    put:
      parameters:
        - in: header
          name: public-key
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/apiV2+json:
            schema:
              type: string
        required: true
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Expected response to a valid request
          content:
            application/hal+json:
              schema:
                properties:
                  lastname:
                    type: string
        default:
          description: unexpected error
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Error"
servers:
- url: http://petstore.swagger.io
components:
  schemas:
    Error:
      required:
      - code
      - message
      properties:
        code:
          type: integer
        message:
          type: string

Error: notImplemented: path "/haljson": put: requestBody: contents: unsupported content types: [application/apiV2+json]
